---
// AboutSection.astro
import kart1 from '../assets/images/kart1.webp';
import kart2 from '../assets/images/kart2.webp';
---

<section id="aboutus" class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-black relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16 lg:gap-24">
      
      <!-- Image Composition (Restored to original slant/skew) -->
      <div class="flex flex-row justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:gap-8 w-full lg:w-1/2 group">
        <!-- Glow effect behind images -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-red-600/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full scale-75 hidden lg:block pointer-events-none"></div>

        <div class="w-32 h-48 sm:w-48 sm:h-64 relative transform skew-x-[-20deg] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-neutral-800/50 hover:border-red-600/50 transition-colors duration-500 z-10">
          <img 
            src={kart1} 
            alt="Kart 1 P1 Speedway" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform skew-x-[20deg] scale-110 hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-700"
            loading="lazy"
          >
        </div>
        <div class="w-32 h-48 sm:w-48 sm:h-64 relative transform skew-x-[-20deg] overflow-hidden mt-6 shadow-2xl border border-neutral-800/50 hover:border-red-600/50 transition-colors duration-500 z-10">
          <img 
            src={kart2} 
            alt="Kart 2 P1 Speedway" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform skew-x-[20deg] scale-110 hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-700"
            loading="lazy"
          >
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col text-center lg:text-left">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start mb-4">
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-red-600"></div>
          <span class="text-red-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Historia & Pasión</span>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tight font-sans">
          P1 <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-red-700">Speedway</span>
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
          P1 Speedway es un proyecto privado dedicado a ofrecer un espacio primer nivel para la práctica de deportes de motor en Costa Rica. 
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
          Nuestra pista fue diseñada específicamente para competencias de kartismo, motovelocidad, minibikes y más, contando con instalaciones aptas para eventos recreativos y corporativos de la más alta calidad. Está construida bajo estándares internacionales, y está lista para llevar tu adrenalina al siguiente nivel.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Highlights/Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-6 border-t border-neutral-900 border-dashed">
          <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
            <span class="block text-3xl font-black text-white mb-1">Avalada</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Estándares FIA</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
            <span class="block text-3xl font-black text-white mb-1">100%</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Adrenalina Pura</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
